<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span
            class="text-[#d4af37] tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-bold uppercase"
            >Nuestros Clientes Dicen</span
        >
        <h3 class="text-[#FAFAF5] font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl mt-3">
            Excelencia Comprobada
        </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {/* Review 1 */}
        <div
            class="bg-[#111111] p-8 rounded-sm relative group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform border border-white/5"
        >
            <div class="flex text-[#d4af37] mb-4">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 italic mb-6 font-light">
                "La calidad es impresionante. Compré una cubana de 5mm y el peso
                es exacto a lo prometido. El envío a Texas fue súper rápido."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-700 overflow-hidden">
                    {/* Placeholder Avatar */}
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-full bg-[#333] flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-white"
                    >
                        CR
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="block text-white text-sm font-bold"
                        >Carlos R.</span
                    >
                    <span class="block text-gray-500 text-xs"
                        >Compra Verificada</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {/* Review 2 */}
        <div
            class="bg-[#111111] p-8 rounded-sm relative group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform border border-white/5"
        >
            <div class="flex text-[#d4af37] mb-4">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 italic mb-6 font-light">
                "Buscaba un regalo especial para mi esposa y el set de
                religiosos le encantó. La presentación es de otro nivel, muy
                lujosa."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-700 overflow-hidden">
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-full bg-[#333] flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-white"
                    >
                        MG
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="block text-white text-sm font-bold"
                        >Maria G.</span
                    >
                    <span class="block text-gray-500 text-xs"
                        >Compra Verificada</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {/* Review 3 */}
        <div
            class="bg-[#111111] p-8 rounded-sm relative group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform border border-white/5"
        >
            <div class="flex text-[#d4af37] mb-4">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 italic mb-6 font-light">
                "Excelente atención. Fui a su oficina en Miami para vender unas
                piezas viejas y me dieron el mejor precio. Súper recomendados."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-700 overflow-hidden">
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-full bg-[#333] flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-white"
                    >
                        JD
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="block text-white text-sm font-bold"
                        >Jorge D.</span
                    >
                    <span class="block text-gray-500 text-xs">Miami, FL</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
